.SH "mINI"
.PP
The â€œmaybe this is not INIâ€ plugin (\fCmini\fP) is a very simple storage plugin loosely based on the \fCINI\fP file format\&. Since this plugin \fBdoes not support sections\fP it might be more appropriate to say that it is based on the \fC\&.properties\fP format, used in many Java applications\&.
.SS "Examples"
.SS "Basic Usage"
